This script adds a link to open a dialog which provides interface for quick view and edit depending on the user's settings.

This script was inspired by the Listing Editor used in many language Wikivoyages and Listing Info in the German Wikivoyage. To use this, your Wikivoyage need to use [[Template:VCard|vCard]] instead of Listing templates. For a document of vCard, please see the German version.

== How to use ==
There are three modes: <code>view</code>, <code>mini</code>, <code>edit</code>. You can change modes on the settings page, which can be opened from the settings button in the lower left corner of the dialog.

